# Test HTTP requests
### use with: REST Client extension
@apiurl = http://localhost:3000/api

### GET all items
GET {{apiurl}}/items

### GET item with id 1
GET {{apiurl}}/items/1

### Add new item
POST {{apiurl}}/items
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "Mandariini", "weight": 86}

### Delete item with id 2
DELETE {{apiurl}}/items/2

### Update item with id 1
PUT {{apiurl}}/items/1
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "updated Omena"}

